{"type":null,"faqId":19867,"title":"G7移动联通双4G版WLAN待机的时候会自动断开，怎么解决，手机默认是什么设置？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>休眠策略的选择会导致此现象出现。进入的方法：在主屏幕，设置 &gt; 无线和网络 &gt; WLAN，再点击菜单键并进入高级 &gt; 在休眠状态下保持WLAN连接，设置为“始终”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>注：手机默认设置是始终，也就是一直可以正常连接。如果调整休眠策略就会使得在待机时自动断开。3个选项的含义如下：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>始终：一直保持WLAN的连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>仅限充电时：只有在充电时才一直保持连接，如果不充电，待机后3分钟断开连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>从不（会增加数据网络流量）：待机后3分钟断开连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>另外，您还可以尝试以下操作进行问题排除：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1. 重新关闭再开启WLAN。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2. 通过右下方虚拟按键进入任务管理器，清除系统缓存内容。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3. 重启手机。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":133,"faqType":"电池与充电","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3207","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Battery-Charging","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1423811150000,"seriesProductName":"G760-UL20","visitedTimes":63,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"G7移动联通双4G版,WLAN,待机,自动,断开","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}